snippet.title: Turkey Soft Tacos
snippet.description: Turkey Soft Tacos will make a delicious, memorable meal and can be put together in minutes. This simple recipe will be a crowd pleaser and is a great way to use turkey leftovers.

snippet.title: Turkey and White Bean Stew
snippet.description: Turkey and White Bean Stew is a perfect way to use up any leftover turkey. With a combination of shredded turkey and white beans, this flavorful stew is perfect for lunch or dinner and is ready in less than 20 minutes.

snippet.title: Turkey Tetrazzini
snippet.description: Turkey Tetrazzini is an easy-to-make meal that is tasty and full of flavor. You'll love the crunchy topping. Ready in less than 1 hour.

snippet.title: Turkey Enchilada Stack
snippet.description: Turkey Enchilada Stack transforms Thanksgiving leftovers in this Mexican-inspired dish featuring layers of turkey, shredded cheese, warm tortillas and homemade enchilada sauce. It'll be 'gobbled' up in no time. Read more about this leftover saving recipe on the Nestlé Kitchens blog .

snippet.title: Take-Two Turkey Tetrazzini
snippet.description: Try something new with leftover turkey with this Take-Two Turkey Tetrazzini. Combine chunks of turkey with a creamy, cheesy sauce and a variety of veggies and bake with al dente spaghetti - it’s a simple dish for all ages to enjoy.

snippet.title: Tacos To Go
snippet.description: For a delicious weeknight meal, simply serve in tortillas with assorted toppings. Or, take it on the go! For those that struggle with school lunches, this is a wonderful solution!

snippet.title: Turkey Veggie Tetrazzini
snippet.description: Turkey Veggie Tetrazzini is a hearty combination of colorful Italian-style vegetables, turkey and whole-wheat spaghetti mixed with a creamy sauce. This updated classic is an easy, yet delicious crowd pleaser.

snippet.title: Smoked Turkey and Tomato Wraps
snippet.description: These flavorful, fresh-tasting Smoked Turkey and Tomato Wraps make a delicious quick lunch or light dinner.

snippet.title: Chicken A La King
snippet.description: Hearty and comforting, Chicken à la King goes equally well over pasta or rice. A healthy alternative to fried chicken.

snippet.title: Turkey & Hash Brown Bake
snippet.description: Delicious Turkey & Hash Brown Bake is quick and easy to make. Just mix the ingredients together, pop in the oven and bake until golden brown. This recipe gets a little extra color from broccoli and extra flavors from Parmesan cheese and Dijon mustard. Ready in just one hour.
